data.description: Welcome to this impressive 2-story home in Gainesville! With 5 bedrooms and 3 baths, this spacious residence offers ample room for your family and guests, making it the ideal place to call home.    Located just a half-mile away from Enota Elementary School, this property is perfect for families with school-age children. You'll enjoy the convenience of being within close proximity to the school, making the daily drop-offs and pick-ups a breeze.    Step inside to discover a home that's truly one-of-a-kind. The unique interior design sets this property apart, adding character and charm to every corner. The attention to detail and creative touches create a warm and inviting atmosphere, making it a space you'll love coming home to.    The finished basement provides additional living space, offering versatility and functionality to suit your lifestyle. Whether you need a playroom for the kids, a home office, or a recreational area, the basement is a blank canvas ready for your personal touch.    Located in a coveted area, this home is close to Riverside Drive, providing easy access to the scenic beauty of the surrounding landscapes. Additionally, downtown Gainesville is just a short drive away, offering a vibrant mix of shops, restaurants, and entertainment options.    Don't miss this opportunity to reside in this exceptional home in a highly sought-after area. Schedule a viewing today and experience the comfort and convenience it has to offer. Possible VA assumable with approval.
